The paper proposes a new texture descriptor for content-based image retrieval, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of genetic algorithm for improving retrieval performance suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The application of the proposed method on multi-resolution images also indicates a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
